title: Miniml Eco White Vinegar Cleaning - All Natural Multi-Surface & Multi-Purpose Cleaner, Limescale Remover, Laundry Softener & More - 100% Vegan & Cruelty Free (5L (Pack of 1)
features: PLANT POWER CLEANING: Easily lift dirt and grime off of any surface with an all natural, non toxic and pure white vinegar 5 Litre for cleaning concentrate. Plant based white vinegar for cleaning is great for glass, floors, work surfaces, bathrooms, etc

MULTIPLE USES: Uses for white vinegar include rinse aid, limescale removal, multi-surface cleaner, laundry softener, stain remover and pet odour remover to name a few. It can even be used in septic tanks or with disinfectant for an even stronger clean

ECO FRIENDLY: Our cleaning vinegar is free from VOC’s, chlorine bleaches, solvents, lanoline, sulphates, parabens and phosphates. However, our strong white vinegar is readily biodegradable but not for stone, marble, granite surfaces or human consumption

STRONG VINEGAR: Our white vinegar thoroughly cleans and cleanses windows, mirrors, dishwasher, toilet, urinal, bidet, work surfaces, kitchen, bathroom, washing machine and carpets without leaving any streaks.

ZERO WASTE: Our eco friendly and fully sustainable solutions go far beyond your purchase. Simply send us back your empty bottles for professional cleaning so that they can be reused again and again. We even have refill partners across the UK to help make the world a cleaner, greener place to live
